@startuml
title After Sales Service - Sequence Diagram

actor Customer as C
participant "Service Portal" as Portal
participant "CRM / Ticket System" as CRM
participant "Service Agent" as Agent
participant "Technician" as Tech
participant "Inventory" as Stock

C -> Portal: Submit service request
Portal -> CRM: Create ticket
CRM -> Agent: Notify new ticket

Agent -> CRM: Review warranty and product history
CRM --> Agent: Customer, product, warranty data

alt Warranty valid
  Agent -> Tech: Assign repair job
  Tech -> CRM: Diagnose issue

  alt Spare part required
    Tech -> Stock: Request spare part
    Stock --> Tech: Confirm availability
  else No spare part required
    Tech -> Tech: Repair or configure product
  end

  Tech -> CRM: Update service result
  CRM -> C: Send repair status
else Warranty expired
  Agent -> C: Send quotation
  C --> Agent: Approve quotation
  Agent -> Tech: Assign paid service job
end

Agent -> CRM: Close ticket
CRM -> C: Send satisfaction survey

@enduml
